Lorenz program controls:
__________________________________
esc || exit
0   || reset view window
-   || zoom out (increase w value)
+   || zoom in (decrease w value)
s   || decrease s value
S   || increase s value
b   || decrease b value
B   || increase b value
r   || decrease r value
R   || increase r value
__________________________________

Arrow keys to rotate view angle
__________________________________
